 This file catalogues mistakes and failure patterns encountered when applying information design rules.  It translates evidence from failure reports into specific triggers, symptoms, and prevention/recovery guidance.  The goal is to reduce recurrence of known problems and improve auditing discipline.
 
+## Scope
+
+- **Covers:** documenting mistakes, failure modes, triggers, symptoms, prevention and recovery actions for information design tasks.
+- **Does not cover:** failure patterns related to prompt design, workflow processes or code execution.
